Introduction

ATT (also known as Asian Twinkle Treasure) was a South Korean girl group under Broad Entertainment. ATT has 5 members: Seohee, Sebi, Seyeon, A Young and Yujeong. The group debuted on October 7th, 2015 with their song ”Temptation”. They disbanded in 2016.
